data.description: Suburban living in the city!!!  This lovely rambler in the Fort Dupont area is ripe for the picking.  Spacious corner lot that offers many possibilities.  You have 4 bedrooms with 3 bathrooms in a quiet section of the city.  The home was recently updated with a new kitchen and bathroom remodels.  Updated stainless steel appliances and more.   The home is located on a large lot with plenty of room to add additional features to the home and/or yard.  Driveway accommodates several vehicles with a curb cut in the rear for additional parking.   Enjoy a finished lower level fit for entertaining.
